Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:35.44,Shadow house-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(359,513)}{\pos(404,876)}不完整的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:37.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喂  傑勒德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:40.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這裡的棋子不動了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:43.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這兩人可是落選候補  給我好好跟蹤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:45.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:51.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我說  要不給愛德華傳句話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:52.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:53.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:21.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,傳來了無聊的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:25.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過這隻黑灰鴿子  就不能安靜地變成文字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有好戲看了  尚恩要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:30.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  原來是陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:49.65,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真是個蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:53.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,地圖上表現不出高低差  這也是一個陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:57.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,看來  果然還是露會最先抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:59.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,等等  這條路線…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要發生有趣的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:13.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露那傢伙  摔壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我沒有想要偷走你的剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:41.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那個…你沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我的臉  沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:51.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,靠…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你靠太近了  我看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:03:59.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:03.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你一點感情都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,剛才那懸崖  真虧你沒掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我抓住藤蔓  懸在了半空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你出血了  不痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:17.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:20.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在那坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好了  這樣就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,只是因為看見你血流個不停  覺得不爽罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:33.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,少得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我擔心的就只有帕利克少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:43.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,現在帕利克少爺一定十分不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可惡  這是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,居然把帕利克關進這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:55.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的愛德華  你等著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,利奇  快來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快來救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你會來救我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:08.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要是你不在  帕利克該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喂  誰來放我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:16.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不要太過分了  別把帕利克關起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這才不是影家人應有的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,討厭  討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:26.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,利奇  利奇…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克少爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這聲音是帕利克少爺對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:38.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請放心吧  我現在就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您好  帕利克少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,能看見我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得你這樣把眼睛貼上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,應該看不見裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,欸  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:55.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你是「花田」…是叫埃米莉可的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:56.17,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:03.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喂  你聽到帕利克剛才的話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:06.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯  非常抱歉  我都聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:09.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了  所以才同情我要來救我什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:13.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我怎麼會接受你這種廢物的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:16.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,滾一邊去  少看不起帕利克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我沒有看不起您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,騙人  你肯定看不起我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:20.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有看不起您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:22.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,煩死了煩死了  快忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我做不到這麼快就忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:30.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒有人願意獨自一人被關在這樣的地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:35.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我都沒有想過影大人居然會被關起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:38.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我好擔心凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:43.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,同樣的  利奇也在擔心帕利克少爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.65,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對了  我來說點利奇的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:51.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,愛德華說了規則是活人偶不能傷到自己的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,所以利奇就選了黑灰外套
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他想得十分周到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對了  影大人不能弄髒衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克少爺也小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我看看  箱子上有鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有一個通氣孔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:09.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,打開鎖的提示在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:13.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,救了帕利克你也過不了測試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,救了也不會落選
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:19.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,能幫上忙我就很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:24.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,夠了  埃米莉可快點去找凱特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:25.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:26.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,別小看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:29.20,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,救帕利克的人是利奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:30.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他肯定會來救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:34.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克不在這裡等著的話就無法做表率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,差點就搶走利奇的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:43.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那至少拿去從洞裡掉進去的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:45.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:49.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:50.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這是橘子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,吃了就有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是路上摘的可愛黃花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:02.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,看著它時間很快就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:04.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:15.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,期待下次和凱特小姐一起與您見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:24.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,花？那傢伙真的是塊「花田」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:41.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,光是門這麼重  就能看出在給我們找麻煩啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:42.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:44.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:48.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,三個人偶在這裡匯合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:50.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩看起來很能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:54.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,多蘿西要是「花田」的話  就會巧妙地利用他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,「花田」沒有這樣的心思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,相反  萊恩要是尚恩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:04.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就會把那兩人關進剛才的重門小屋  讓她們一口氣掉隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:07.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過關進去就太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我想看表情啊  陷入絕望時的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:12.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:17.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒看資料嗎  這三個人偶關係很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:21.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,本來你們也不是尚恩或者埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:24.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我就是不喜歡這傢伙的這點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,地圖上表示影大人的點下面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有著像是文字的線條
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我眼神不好  看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:33.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你看得清嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這不是文字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:37.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這是線條吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得那麼小的文字是寫不上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們來互相講講走過的路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,雖然我也在意黑點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但想先和埃米莉可匯合  就來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:55.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,比起一個人前往傳來爆炸聲的方向  這樣子更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這個點是帕利克少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:01.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得爆炸聲是從影大人所在地傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我在高處看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:04.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:06.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我很擔心  所以接下來就去那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:07.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:11.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沿著路以最短距離全部繞一圈的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:15.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就只能通過現在這個地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,又是謎題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,地圖上沒有任何標記
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,鐵柵欄上也沒有像是鎖孔的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩能翻過這堵牆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:33.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不行  牆的另一邊能看見種有長滿棘刺的樹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:37.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,而且難得匯合了  就一起通過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:48.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,果然這些動物雕像最可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:52.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,和台座之間有縫隙？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:55.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這個轉得動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:01.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,泥水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,捉弄人的機關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對不起  尚恩  弄髒你的臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,知道這雕像可以動  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,肯定有哪個是鐵柵欄的開關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:18.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過  如果猜錯了  就會遇上像剛才那樣的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,說不定會有弄傷臉的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:25.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,還是要繞遠道  避開這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.17,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你想太多了  尚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:32.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,總之先坐在長椅上  吃點橘子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你還是和往常一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這是在溫室摘的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:38.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,多了好多行李
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爬坡的話會很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:41.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,已經爬過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:46.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,坐下的…重量？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:47.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:51.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,雕像只是假象  長椅的重量才是開關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:54.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,而且還正好能坐三個人  我們一起坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有發生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:04.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,確實  即使和影大人一組也只是兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒有理由要三個人一起坐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,三個人一起坐是尚恩提的主意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:15.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那個  在庭院裡這種長椅叫做坐席
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:18.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,它會放在讓人觀景的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,風景的確很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:24.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那邊的樹和前後的樹重疊起來  看起來就像兔子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:30.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,究竟發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:42.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,黑灰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:44.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這裡有腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.17,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這個大小…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是喬恩少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:50.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:54.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他掉進陷阱裡了嗎  還是被誰怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:56.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,視野很差  腳印也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:09.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,能自己走就說明他沒事  可能只是散步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:13.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,說的也是  喬恩少爺挺隨心所欲的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:16.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是亡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:20.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊  原來是園藝的裝飾建築  你別嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,裝飾建築？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那是人造品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:25.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,庭院裡會擺放像這樣沒什麼意義的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有時還會放些惡趣味的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:32.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好大  可以爬上去耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們制定計劃  你先去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:35.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:39.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,假設喬恩少爺在散步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:42.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這種地形  要是錯過了再找就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,每個人分開找會更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:48.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可從它的頭髮裡登場啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:53.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是從我的出發地到喬恩少爺的所在地其實很近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:55.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,剛才只顧著解謎了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,畢竟我去了埃米莉可那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩你就是會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:04.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩少爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:04.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您為什麼會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:08.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你問我為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因為這個裝飾很大  可以爬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:14.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您是怎麼從箱子裡出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:22.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,黑灰很厲害哦  不  應該說喬恩很厲害才對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:29.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  我一氣之下  砰地一下轟隆地一下就出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩少爺黑灰的力量也很強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:34.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩少爺  您的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影大人弄髒了衣服就會失去資格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真的假的  這可沒人告訴喬恩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:48.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.44,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:54.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影家人原本就會冒黑灰  衣服會被慢慢弄髒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:58.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,更何況是被關在那麼狹窄的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:01.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑啊  愛德華
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩要用自己的力量吹走衣服上的黑灰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩少爺  會弄得更髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:11.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,他居然隱瞞這種情報  對我們也太不利了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:13.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我得去告訴剛剛碰到的凱特才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您見到凱特小姐了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.95,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩可是立志向上的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:23.83,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:28.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  選擇向上的路就能見到凱特小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:33.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  從剛才開始你怎麼一下就理解了喬恩少爺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:37.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,然後  喬恩在那裡和凱特聊了聊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:40.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:46.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,未婚妻？  影宅之王？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,別說了  喬恩也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那些話真的是蠢到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:55.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我原本沒打算這麼唐突地說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:58.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,可是  我緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:02.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩少爺緊張的時候  膽子就會變大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:05.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請您不要失落  吃點橘子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,地圖可不是餐巾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:11.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,說起來  埃米莉可是凱特的「臉」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:12.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:15.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,剛才的話不要跟凱特說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:15.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:17.98,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請吃橘子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:25.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,雖然你像妹妹一樣可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:28.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但作為凱特的臉  我覺得還是有點稚嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:32.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過  喬恩喜歡的是凱特的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,而且黑灰也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:39.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,並且  單看「臉」也能明白凱特的心靈美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:42.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,畢竟從培養「臉」的方式能看出這個人自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:46.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說  凱特也有像埃米莉可一樣可愛的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:50.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,高貴與可愛的結合體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:52.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過  先不說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:56.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  要救凱特可不簡單哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:03.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  凱特小姐被關在了那麼可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊  這不是能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,表情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩  請借給我放大鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我要好好確認找凱特小姐的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:20.41,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這裡好暗  拉姆  請借給我燈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:27.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來  放大鏡真好玩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,啊  地圖上有隻螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:31.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不要玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:34.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,太樂觀也是她的魅力之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:40.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我知道之前尚恩在意的  黑點下的暗號的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:45.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,仔細看的話  並不是一條線  它有分開的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:49.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這個數好像能和我們在大廳時的排位對應上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:53.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,帕利克少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:55.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,露薏絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:57.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,夏麗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:17:59.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:03.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就知道全部影大人的所在地了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,太好了  拉姆  夏麗大人就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:12.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,太靠近提燈  地圖被燒焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是燒出來的圖案好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,燒焦的是地圖上滴到橘子汁的部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:21.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這邊焦的地方有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,用我的地圖來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:27.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩看了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:28.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩少爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:32.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,做得好  拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:36.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這塊浮現深色的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是高低差
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:41.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就能充分理解道路的連接方式了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:47.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,接下來就是確認黑灰沙漏  我們去看看剩下的時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:50.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,黑灰沙漏  黑灰沙漏…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,剩下五十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:19:00.74,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她說黑灰沙漏的分量和我們走過的距離她都記得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:04.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就算不看也能計算出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好厲害  居然能做到這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:11.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,之後就是  喬恩少爺滿是黑灰的衣服要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:15.46,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,出口附近會不會準備好了更換的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:18.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,再說了  我的衣服也沒有那麼髒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,很髒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:23.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,真麻煩  要不我去把愛德華打一頓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:26.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請等一下  也許有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,黑灰避開了那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,去那裡看看吧  尚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:37.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是  但是這張地圖看不到其他的訊息了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:48.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,她說地圖上的訊息她都記住了  地圖可以給尚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,全部都記住了？  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:51.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對了  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:56.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,關於找凱特的路線  我有話跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.64,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,喬恩去的時候走過的橋已經斷掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:01.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:03.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我一看橋邊寫著的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:06.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,上面寫著「僅限過兩次」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:09.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,所以說  我們走下面的超級迷宮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:12.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,看得我好暈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:16.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不就是因為喬恩少爺轉來轉去  事情才變得這麼麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:20.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩  你說話越來越沒大沒小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:21.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:25.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒事  這樣就很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:29.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,去出口的路只有下面走的這一條
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:31.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣一來  凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,夏麗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:34.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,出口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,接下來我們要走的線路是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:41.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不對  尚恩還是從我們來的右側道路回去更好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:47.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,去找凱特小姐的路看起來並不簡單  我也想幫埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:49.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你已經幫了我許多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.85,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,注意到黑點下的線的是尚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:56.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,剛才的長椅  是叫坐席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:21:01.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,如果你沒說在那裡看風景  我也不會注意到兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:07.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因為有尚恩  拉姆  和喬恩少爺  我才能走到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:13.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影大人要由自己的活人偶救出  這是帕利克少爺告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:17.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,尚恩必須要救出喬恩少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:23.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:28.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那麼埃米莉可  我們就在這裡分別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:28.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:31.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,拉姆  說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:34.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,一開始我還以為你是個遲疑不決  死氣沉沉的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:38.20,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是我錯了  拉姆有能力有毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:53.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,各位  一定要通過「露面」再次相見
